quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  40,21,"Shibachendangakhwo khushialo mana balola indukho yabalia bali imbeli wabu, bali nende amani amanji okhubashila, nende ebikhole ebikhongo khushialo, mana Nyasaye nabatila obutinyu khutsimbi tsiabu, mana nibakhaywa ubakhoonya okhurula khushinyasio shia Nyasaye"
  40,22,"Endio nilwokhuba mbu Abarumwa babetselanga nende ebifune biyela mana nibakhaya ne Nyasaye nabatila, toto ye niwa amaani weshinyasio eshilulu"
  40,23,Ne toto khwaruma Musa halala nende ebimanyisio biefu nende ebifune bia habulafu
  40,24,"Khu Firaun nende Hamana nende Qarun, mana nibaboola mbu : “uno ni Omulosi Omubeeyi muno.”"
  40,25,"Olwa yabeetsela nende obwatoto okhurula khwifwe , baboola mbu: “yire Abana abasiani babalia basuubila ninaye , mana muleshe Abana abakhana, ne ebifwanga bia bakhayi shibli hosi hosi tawe halali mubukori.”"
  40,26,"Ne Firaun naboola mbu : “mundeshe ndire Musa mana alanje Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, esie eritsanga ye okhukalukhania idini yenyu nohomba akhole amabii khushialo.”"
  40,27,"Ne Musa naboola mbu: “esie ndilinda khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi khu enywe, okhurulana nende buli Omufuuru ulasuubilanga inyanga yokhubalilwa”"